    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334040/extras/c269b7376177d93a1b0c0acc7f7d9355.webp?t=1764307759\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《街》的故事发生在上世纪80年代的一座边境小城里，主人公李明来正在参与一场重要行动。一次稀松平常的归乡省亲之旅，竟引出一连串无比诡异的事件，李明来最深爱的妻子也下落不明。曾经温馨幸福的家里，如今只剩下一堆谜团，而这些谜团都指向一个叫“阴阳街”的地方。这究竟是巧合还是阴谋？李明来已经无暇思考了，他唯一能做的，便是赶赴“阴阳街”，探寻那无底的深渊……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334040/extras/1e7f877352c0d500aebf47e4b92d45d4.poster.avif?t=1764307759\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334040/extras/1e7f877352c0d500aebf47e4b92d45d4.webm?t=1764307759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334040/extras/1e7f877352c0d500aebf47e4b92d45d4.mp4?t=1764307759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334040/extras/8cb0e23b1b0f6588551c05286259d8ac.webp?t=1764307759\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以上世纪80年代的手绘风格作为美术主基调，带玩家踏上一段怀旧之旅。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >错综复杂的人物关系，环环相扣的五个章节，为玩家带来一个跌宕起伏的悬疑故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻度解谜搭配刺激逃生，增强沉浸感，从各个层面激发玩家内心的恐惧。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334040/extras/be0190b65ebcb51db4a61bd67816bb39.poster.avif?t=1764307759\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334040/extras/be0190b65ebcb51db4a61bd67816bb39.webm?t=1764307759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334040/extras/be0190b65ebcb51db4a61bd67816bb39.mp4?t=1764307759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334040/extras/9e66eebf54c566e6b434bc274bb5cc01.webp?t=1764307759\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大家好，我们是彼云工作室，一个来自云南的独立游戏开发团队。本作以云南民俗文化为背景，我们希望大家能有耳目一新的体验，也恳请大家提供宝贵建议助我们日益精进，非常感谢！</p>",
